    <item>
      <title>德国领跑者梅尔茨警告企业不要投资中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/german-front-runner-warns-companies-against-investing-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在德国下届总理竞选中处于领先地位的保守派弗里德里希·梅尔茨警告国内企业不要在中国进行大规模投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/german-front-runner-warns-companies-against-investing-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 14:54:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保加利亚因通胀未达标而推迟采用欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/bulgaria-tempers-euro-adoption-push-on-inflation-criterion-miss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚新成立的政府将推迟采取采用欧元的下一步措施，直到这个巴尔干国家正式满足欧盟要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/bulgaria-tempers-euro-adoption-push-on-inflation-criterion-miss</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 14:33:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统签署土地征用法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-african-president-signs-off-on-land-expropriation-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨同意一项新法律，该法律使国家可以更容易地为了公共利益征用土地，但必须支付公平的补偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/south-african-president-signs-off-on-land-expropriation-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 14:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普经济风险下马丁重返爱尔兰总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰共和党领袖迈克尔·马丁 (Micheal Martin) 在去年 11 月的选举中当选为总理，主要现任执政联盟伙伴重新执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/ireland-s-martin-returns-as-prime-minister-for-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的农业选择表明她将尊重所有燃料来源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-s-agriculture-pick-set-for-senate-hot-seat-over-biofuels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统提名的美国农业监管人曾经是一个团体的负责人，而该团体是美国最受欢迎的农产品——生物燃料的最强烈反对者之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-s-agriculture-pick-set-for-senate-hot-seat-over-biofuels</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
